The [[Whaladon Meat Quality Control Division]] was a division of [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Dunwell]]'s [[Whaladon/Legends|Whaladon]]-hunting operation that presumably controlled the quality of the Whaladon meat. Meat was shipped there from the [[Whaladon Processing Center]] on [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]] after being chopped into slabs.

